  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Angry Youth</i> is a fighting game that takes place in the mid-1990s, inspired by games like <i>Virtua Fighter,</i> <i>Tekken </i>and<i> Fighting Vipers</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes place in 1995 in the city of Sancatown, where 6 boys, influenced by fighting video games, decide to hold a fighting tournament in the neighborhood where they live. Choose your fighter and let the fighting begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SIMPLE AND FUN GAMEPLAY</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 PLAYABLE CHARACTERS, EACH ONE WITH THEIR OWN FIGHTING STYLE AND PERSONALITY</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 KINDS OF ARENAS</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 GAME MODES</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GUARANTEED FUN FOR EVERYONE</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VIRTUA FIGHTER STYLE CONTROLS (GUARD-PUNCH-KICK)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Angry Youth</i> is a fighting game that takes place in the mid-1990s, inspired by games like <i>Virtua Fighter,</i> <i>Tekken </i>and<i> Fighting Vipers</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes place in 1995 in the city of Sancatown, where 6 boys, influenced by fighting video games, decide to hold a fighting tournament in the neighborhood where they live. Choose your fighter and let the fighting begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SIMPLE AND FUN GAMEPLAY</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 PLAYABLE CHARACTERS, EACH ONE WITH THEIR OWN FIGHTING STYLE AND PERSONALITY</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 KINDS OF ARENAS</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 GAME MODES</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GUARANTEED FUN FOR EVERYONE</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VIRTUA FIGHTER STYLE CONTROLS (GUARD-PUNCH-KICK)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
